data.description:
Welcome to your ideal home! This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence with a garage offers comfort and convenience. 

Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan living space, perfect for entertaining guests or unwinding after a long day. Upstairs, you'll find the primary bedroom and two additional bedrooms, each equipped with attached walk-in closets, providing ample storage space for your belongings. Situated just minutes away from 485, shopping, dining, the airport, and the Whitewater Center, this property offers easy access to all your desired amenities.

Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Schedule a showing today and embrace the epitome of comfortable and convenient living!
